<p><center><u><b>Sonic HQ News Press</b></u>
<br>Your Daily Dose Of Sonic!</center>
<br>
Welcome to the best Sonic news source on the net!  This page will generally be updated everyday.  As a rule, you must give us a link credit if you want to take news reported by us. For those of whom english is not your first language, if you wish to translate any of the news articles into a different language (ie French, Spanish etc), the option is located below. ^_^ Thank you.

<p>Click <a href=edititem.cgi?id=new&series=sonic>here</a> to post your own news!  Be sure to read the intro and rules if it's your first time posting. STRICT Screening will be enforced.

